    <item>
      <title>盈利季节开始前，银行的对冲成本较低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/banks-hedges-are-cheap-before-the-start-of-the-earnings-season</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通、富国银行和花旗集团将于周五拉开美国银行财报季的序幕，交易员们对此感到相当放松。]]></description>
